Well after a whole bunch of faf switching over to my new computer, waiting to transfer all my games off my old one, and playing the password runaround of all requiring sites, I am finally ready to start posting some of the spacecraft that I've made over the years and thought were too good not to share. Lucky you guys!

 

P.S. If this isn't the correct place to post this, tell me and I'll move it to the correct place, I'm new at this whole forum thing.

Thanks, I'll be starting an 80's Space Shuttle Program themed mission series soon*.
